item.title: gitのssh設定
item.description: 秘密・公開鍵の作成 $ cd ~/.ssh $ ssh-keygen -t rsa Generating public/private rsa key pair. Enter file in which to save the key (/Users/(username)/.ssh/id_rsa):id_rsa_for_git Enter passphrase (empty for no passphrase): Enter same passphrase again: githubにてkeyの登録 settings にて行う ssh configの作成 $
